                    <p class="mt-0 wow fadeIn">
                    <span class="bold pink">And the best</span> there‚Äôs only one way to run an operation.
                    Any dependency, such as the <code>current_user</code>, must be injected from the outside.
                    </p>
                    <p class="mt-0 wow fadeIn">
                    The concept of global state does not exist in Trailblazer, which leads to simplified, mock-free testability and concurrent-ready code.
                    </p>
                  </div>
                  <div class="col-md-6">
                    <pre><code class="ruby dark code-snippet wow fadeIn d-block">
